* Simon Anglim, ''[http://reading.academia.edu/SimonAnglim/Papers/703710/Orde_Wingate_and_Anglo-Jewish_Military_Cooperation_in_Palestine_-_Myth_versus_Reality Orde Wingate and Anglo-Jewish Military Cooperation in Palestine - Myth versus Reality]'', Résumé d'une conférence tenue au King's College de Londre, 2008. {{plume}}

